The paper is about mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT) and theoretical computer science (cs.EC). The paper also discusses the efficiency of mechanisms, which is related to optimization (cs.DS) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper's focus on smooth and weakly smooth mechanisms also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG).
